Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的誓言無法作假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修·蘭佩洛奇的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為母親報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並創造一個妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他獲得了Geass的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他化身為ZERO而行動著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少
